hadiths[94]{hadithnumber,text}:
5373,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke bhookey ko khilaao-pulaao, bimar ki mizaaj pursi karo aur qaidi ko chhudaao. Sufiyan Sory ne kaha ke (hadees mein) lafz ( عاني ( se murad qaidi hai."
5374,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat tak aal Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par kabhi aisa zamana nahi guzra ke kuchh din barabar unhon-ne pet bhar ke khana khaya ho aur isi sanad se.
5375,"unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( bayan kya ke faaqe ki wjah se) mein sakht mashaqqat mein mubtala tha, phir meri mulaqat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se hui aur unse maine Quran Majeed ki aik aayat padhney ke liye kaha, unhon-ne mujhey wo aayat padh kar sunai aur phir apne ghar mein dakhil ho gaey. iske baad main bahut door tak chalta raha. aakhir mashaqqat aur bhook ki wjah se main munh ke bal gir padaa . achcha maine dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere sar ke paas khadey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey Abu-Hurera ! maine kaha hazir hun, ya Rasulullah ! taiyaar hun. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mera hath pakad kar mujhey khada kya. aap samajh gaey ke main kis takleef mein mubtala hun. phir aap mujhey apne ghar le gaey aur mere liye doodh ka aik bada piyala mangwaayaa. maine usmein doodh piyaa . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke dobara piyo ( Abu-Hurera ! ( maine dobara piyaa . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aur piyo . maine aur piyaa . yahan tak ke mera pet bhi piyaale ki tarah bharpur ho gaya. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) se mila aur unse apna Sara waqia bayan kya aur kaha ke aey umr ! Allah Taala ne usey us zaat ke zariey pura kara diya, jo aap se zyada mustahiq thi. Allah ki qism ! maine tum se aayat poochhi thi halanke main usey tum se bhi zyada behtar tareeqe par padh sakta tha. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! agar maine tum ko apne ghar mein dakhil kar liya hota aur tum ko khana khilaa deta to laal laal (umda ( oont milney se bhi zyada mujh ko khushi hoti."
5376,"main bachcha tha aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki parwarish mein tha aur (khaatey waqt) mera hath bartan mein charon taraf ghoomaa karta. isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya ke betey ! bismillaah padh liya karo, daahiney hath se khaya karo aur bartan mein wahan se khaya karo jo jagah tujh se nazdeek ho. chunanche iske baad mein hamesha usi hidayat ke mutabiq khata raha."
5377,aik din maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath khana khaya aur bartan ke charon taraf se khaney laga to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya ke apne nazdeek se khaa.
5378,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein khana laya gaya, aap ke sath aap ke rabeeb (parwarish mein rahnewaalaa) Umar-bin-abii-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke bismillaah padh aur apne samney se khaa."
5379,"aik darzii ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khaney ki dawat ki jo unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye taiyaar kya tha. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath mein bhi gaya, maine dekha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) piyaale mein charon taraf kadu talash kartey they (khaaney ke liye) bayan kya ke isi din se kadu mujh ko bhi bahut bhaaney laga."
5380,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jahan tak mumkin hota paakii hasil karne mein, jootaa pahnney aur kangha karne mein dahini taraf se shuruaat kartey. Ashas us hadis ka rawi jab waasit Shahar mein tha to usne us hadis mein yun kaha tha ke har aik kaam main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dahini taraf se shuruaat kartey."
5381,"abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni biwi Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki awaz mein zauf w naqahat ko mehsus kya hai aur malum hota hai ke aap faaqe se hain. kya tumharey paas koi cheez hai? chunanche unhon-ne jau ki chand rotiyaan nikaaliin, phir apna dupatta nikala aur uske aik hisse mein rotiyon ko lapet kar mere (yani Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ke) kapdey ke nichey chipa diya aur aik hissey mujhey chadar ki tarah odha diya, phir mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein bhejaa. bayan kya ke main jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to aapko masjid mein paya aur aap ke sath sahaba they. main un sab hazraat ke samney ja kar khada ho gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke aey Anas! tumhen abu-Talha ne bheja hoga. maine kaha ji haan. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : khaney ke saath? maine arz ki, ji haan. iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne sathiyon se farmaya ke khadey ho jao . chunanche aap rawaana huey. mein sab ke aagey-aagey chalta raha. jab abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas wapas pahuncha to unhon-ne kaha : Umme-Sulaim! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sahaba ko sath lekar tashrif laey hain, halanke hamarey paas khaney ka itna saman nahi jo sab ko kafi ho sakey. Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) is par boliin ke Allah aur uska rasool khub jantey hain. bayan kya ke phir abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) (istiqbaal ke liye) nikley aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mulaqat ki. iske baad abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghar ki taraf mutwajjeh huey aur ghar mein dakhil ho gaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Umme-Sulaim ! jo kuchh tumharey paas hai wo yahan laao. Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) roti laaein , Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya aur uska chooraa kar liya gaya. Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne ghi ke dabbe mein se ghi nichod kar uska maleeda bana liya, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua ki jo kuchh Allah Taala ne aap se dua karaanii chaahii, iske baad farmaya ke un das das aadmiyon ko khaney ke liye bula lo. chunanche das sahaba ko bulaya. sab ne khaya aur pet bhar kar bahar chaley gaey. phir farmaya ke das ko aur bula lo, unhein bulaya gaya aur sab ne pet bhar kar khaya aur bahar chaley gaey. phir aap ne farmaya ke das sahaba ko aur bula lo, phir das sahaba ko bulaya gaya aur un logon ne bhi khub pet bhar kar khaya aur bahar tashrif ley gaey. iske baad phir das sahaba ko bulaya gaya is tarah tamam sahaba ne pet bhar kar khaayaa, us waqt usi ( 80 ( sahaba ki jamat wahan maujood thi."
5382,"ham aik so tees aadmi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke tum mein se kisi ke paas khana hai. aik sahib ne apne paas se aik saa ke qareeb aata nikaalaa, usey goondh liya gaya, phir aik mushrik lambaa-tadangaa apni bakriyan haanktaa hua udhar aa gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se malum farmaya ke ye bechney ki hain ya Atiya hain ya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (atiya ke bajaey) hiba farmaya, us shakhs ne kaha ke nahi balke bechney ki hain. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se aik bakri kharidi phir zabah ki gaee aur aap ne uski kalejii bhooney janey ka hukm diya aur qism Allah ki aik so tees logon ki jamat mein koi shakhs aisa nahi raha jisey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us bakri ki kalejii ka eik-eik tukda kaat kar na diya ho magar wo maujood tha to usey wahin de diya aur agar wo maujood nahi tha to uska hissey mehfooz rakhaa, phir us bakri ke gosht ko pakka kar do badey koondon mein rakha aur ham sab ne unmein se pet bhar kar khaya phir bhi donon koondon mein khana bach gaya to maine usey oont par laad liya. Abdur-Rehman rawi ne aisa hi koi kalima kahaa."
5383,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat hui, un dinon ham pani aur khajoor se sair ho janey lagey they."
5384,"ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath khaibar ki taraf ( 7 hijri mein) nikley jab ham maqam Sahbaa par pahunchey . Yahya ne bayan kya ke Sahbaa khaibar se do-pahar ki raah par hai to us waqt Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khana talab farmaya lekin sattu ke siwa aur koi cheez nahi laai gaee, phir ham ne usi ko sookhaa phaank liya. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pani talab farmaya aur kulli ki, ham ne bhi kulli ki. iske baad aap ne hamein maghrib ki Namaz padhai aur wuzu nahi kya (maghrib ke liye kyonke pahley se baa-wuzoo they). Sufiyan ne bayan kya ke maine Yahya se us hadis mein yun suna ke aap ne na sattu khaatey waqt wuzu kya na khaney se farigh ho kar."
5385,"ham Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein baithey huey they, us waqt unka roti pakaaney wala khaadim bhi maujood tha. unhon-ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kabhi chapaatii (maida ki rotii) nahi khaaii aur na saari dam-pukhta bakri khaaii yahan tak ke aap Allah se ja miley."
5386,mein nahi janta ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kabhi tashtarii rakh kar (eik waqt mukhtalif qism ka ( khana khaya ho aur na kabhi aap ne patlii rotiyaan (chapaatiyaan) khaaiin aur na kabhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mez par khaayaa. Qatada se puchha gaya ke phir kis cheez par aap khaatey they? kaha ke aap (aam dastar-khuwaan) par khana khaya kartey they.
5387,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) se nikah ke baad unke sath rastey mein qiyam kya aur maine musalmanon ko aap ke walima ki dawat mein bulaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dastar-khuwaan bichhaaney ka hukm diya aur wo bichhaayaa gaya, phir aap ne is par khajoor, paneer aur ghi daal diya aur Amr bin abi Amr ne kaha, unse Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath sohbat ki, phir aik chamdey ke dastar-khuwaan par (khajoor, ghii, paneer mila kar bana hua) halwa rakha."
5388,"ahale-Shaam (Syria) (Hujjaaj-bin-Yoosuf ke faujii) Sham (Syria) ke log Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ko aar dilaane ke liye kehney lagey ''yaa ibn-zaatun-naqaatein''aey 2 kamar band wali ke betey aur unki waalida, Asma (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha, aey betey! ye tumhen 2 kamar band wali ki aar dilaatey hain, tumhen malum hai wo kamar band kya they? wo mera kamar band tha jiske maine 2 tukdey kar diye they aur aik tukdey se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke bartan ka munh baandha tha aur doosrey se dastar-khuwaan banaya (is mein khane-pine ka saman lapetaa). Wahab ne bayan kya ke phir jab Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ko ahale-Shaam (Syria) 2 kamar band wali ki aar dilaatey they, to wo kehtey haan. Allah ki qasam! ye beshak sach hai aur wo ye misra'a padhtey ( تلك شكاة ظاهر عنك عارها) ye to waisaa ta'na hai jis mein kuchh aib nahi hai."
5389,"Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki khala umme-Hufaid-binte-Haaris-bin-huzn (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ghii, paneer aur saahina hadiya ke taur par bhejii. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aurton ko bulaya aur unhon-ne aap ke dastar-khuwaan par saahina ko khaya lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey hath bhi nahi lagaya jaisey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usey na-pasand kartey hain. lekin agar saahina haram hota to aap ke dastar-khuwaan par khaya na jata aur na aap unhein khaney ke liye farmatey."
5390,wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath maqam sahbaa mein they. wo khaibar se aik manzil par hai. Namaz ka waqt qareeb tha to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khana talab farmaya lekin sattu ke siwa aur koi cheez nahi laai gaee. aakhir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usko phaank liya aur ham ne bhi phaankaa phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pani talab farmaya aur kulli ki. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhai aur ham ne bhi aap ke sath Namaz padhi aur aap ne (is Namaz ke liye nayaa) wuzu nahi kya.
5391,"mujhey abu-Umaama-bin-Sahal-bin-Haneef Ansari ne khabar di, unhein Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di aur unhein Khalid-bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ne jo saifullaah ( Allah ki talwaar (ke laqab se mashhoor hain, khabar di ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Ummul-Momenin Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar mein dakhil huey. Ummul-Momenin unki aur Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki khala hain. unke yahan bhunaa hua saahina maujood tha jo unki behan Hufaida binte- al-Haaris (Raziallahu anhu) Najad se laai thin. unhon-ne wo bhunaa hua saahina Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kya. aisa bahut kam hota tha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi khaney ke liye us waqt tak hath badhaayein jab tak aapko iske mutaalliq bata na diya jaey ke ye falan khana hai lekin us din aap ne bhuney huey saahiney ke gosht ki taraf hath badhaayaa. itney mein wahan maujood aurton mein se aik aurat ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bata kyon nahi detiin ke us waqt aap ke samney jo tum ne pesh kya hai wo saahina hai, ya Rasulullah! (ye sun kar) aap ne apna hath saahina se hata liya. Khaalid-bin-Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) boley ke ya Rasulullah ! kya saahina haram hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi lekin ye mere mulk mein chunkey nahi paya jata, isliye tabeeat pasand nahi karti . Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir maine usey apni taraf kheench liya aur usey khaayaa. us waqt Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujhey dekh rahe they."
5392,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke 2 aadmiyon ka khana teen ke liye kafi hai aur teen ka char ke liye kafi hai.
5393,"ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) us waqt tak khana nahi khaatey they, jab tak unke sath khaney ke liye koi miskeen na laya jata. aik martaba mein unke sath khaney ke liye aik shakhs ko laya ke usne bahut zyada khana khaayaa. baad mein ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke aainda us shakhs ko mere sath khaney ke liye na lana . maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai ke momin aik aant mein khata aur kaafir saaton aantein bhar leta hai."
5394,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke momin aik aant mein khata hai aur kaafir ya munafiq (abda ne kaha ke) mujhey yaqin nahi ke unmein se kis ke mutaalliq Ubaidullah ne bayan kya ke wo saaton aantein bhar leta hai aur ibne-Bukair ne bayan kya, unse Imam Malik ne bayan kya, unse Naafe ne, unse ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usi hadis ki tarah bayan farmaayaa."
5395,Abu-Nuhaik badey khaney waley they. unse Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya hai ke kaafir saaton aanton mein khata hai. Abu-Nuhaik ne is par arz kya ke main Allah aur uske rasool par eman rakhta hun.
5396,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke musalman aik aant mein khata hai aur kaafir saaton aanton mein khata hai.
5397,"aik sahib bahut zyada khana khaya kartey they, phir wo Islam laey to kam khaney lagey. iska zikr Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke momin aik aant mein khata hai aur kaafir saaton aanton mein khata hai."
5398,"maine abu-Juhaifa (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main tek laga kar nahi khata ."
5399,main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik sahabi se jo aap ke paas maujood they farmaya ke main tek laga kar nahi khata .
5400,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye bhunaa hua saahina pesh kya gaya to aap usey khaney ke liye mutwajjeh huey. usi waqt aapko bataya gaya ke ye saahina hai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna hath rok liya. Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha kya ye haram hai? farmaya ke nahi lekin chunkey ye mere mulk mein nahi hota isliye tabeeat usey gawara nahi karti . phir Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey khaya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dekh rahe they. Imam Malik ne ibne-Shahab se ( ضب محنوذ‏ . Mina ( (yani bhunaa hua saahina ( ضب مشوی ( ki jagah ( محنوذ‏) naql kya, donon lafzon ka aik mana hai)."
5401,"Utban bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba mein se they aur qabila Ansar ke un logon mein se they jinhoney badr ki ladai mein shirkat ki thi. aap Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya ke ya Rasulullah! meri nigaah kamzor hai aur main apni qaum ko Namaz padhaataa hun. barsat mein wadi jo mere aur unke darmyan haail hai, bahney lagti hai aur mere liye unki masjid mein jana aur unmein Namaz padhna mumkin nahi rahtaa. isliye ya Rasulullah ! meri ye khahish hai ke aap mere ghar tashrif ley chalein aur mere ghar mein aap Namaz padhein taake main usi jagah ko Namaz padhney ki jagah bana loon. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke inshaAllah mein jald hi aisa karunga . Utban (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath chasht ke waqt jab suraj kuchh buland ho gaya tashrif laey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne andar aaney ki ijazat chaahi. maine aapko ijazat de di. aap baithey nahi balke ghar mein dakhil ho gaey aur malum farmaya ke apne ghar mein kis jagah tum pasand kartey ho ke main Namaz padhun ? maine ghar ke aik koney ki taraf ishara kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wahan khadey ho gaey aur (namaz ke liye) takbeer kahi . ham ne bhi (aap ke peechhey ( saf bana li. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khazeera ( Hurera ki aik qism) ke liye jo aap ke liye ham ne banaya tha rok liya. ghar mein qabeele ke bahut se log aa aa kar jama ho gaey. unmein se aik sahib ne kaha Maalik-bin-dakhshan kahan hain? is par kisi ne kaha ke wo to munafiq hai Allah aur uske rasool se usey mohabbat nahi hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye na kaho, kya tum nahi dekhtey ke unhon-ne iqrar kya hai ke) لا إله إلا الله ( yani Allah ke siwa aur koi maabood nahi aur us se unka maqsad sirf Allah ki khushnoodii hasil karna hai. un sahabi ne kaha ke Allah aur uske rasool hi zyada jantey hain. rawi ne bayan kya ke ham ne arz kya (ya rasoolullaah!) lekin ham unki tawajjoh aur unka lagaao munaafeqeen ke sath hi dekhtey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : lekin Allah ne dozakh ki aag ko us shakhs par haram kar diya hai jisne kalima ( لا إله إلا الله (ka iqrar kar liya ho aur us se iska maqsad Allah ki khushnoodii ho. ibne-Shahab ne bayan kya ke phir maine Husain bin-Muhammad Ansari se jo bani Salim ke aik fard aur unke sardaar they. Mehmood ki hadis ke mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne uski tasdeeq ki."
5402,"meri khala ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein saahina ka gosht, paneer aur doodh hadiyatan pesh kya to saahina ka gosht aap ke dastar-khuwaan par rakha gaya aur agar saahina haram hota to aap ke dastar-khuwaan par nahi rakha ja sakta tha lekin aap ne doodh piyaa aur paneer khaayaa."
5403,"hamein Juma ke din badi khushi rehti thi. hamari aik boodhi khatun thin wo chuqandar ki jadein lekar apni handi mein pakaatii thin, uper se kuchh daney jau ke usmein daal deti thin. ham Juma ki Namaz padh kar unki mulaqat ko jatey to wo hamarey samney ye khana rakhti thin. Juma ke din hamein badi khushi isi wjah se rehti thi. ham Namaz Juma ke baad hi khana khaya kartey they. Allah ki qasam! na usmein charbi hoti thi na ghi aur jab bhi ham mazey se usko khaatey."
5404,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne shaaney ki haddi ka gosht khaayaa, phir khadey huey aur Namaz padhi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (namaz ke liye nayaa) wuzu nahi kya aur (usi sanad se) ."
5405,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne paktii hui handiya mein se adh kachchi buti nikaalii aur usey khaya phir Namaz padhai aur nayaa wuzu nahi kya.
5406,ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Makka ki taraf nikley (Suleh Hudaibiya ke mauqe par) dusri sanad ( hadis dekhein 5407 (
5407,"mein aik din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chand sahaba ke sath Makka ke raaste mein aik manzil par betha hua tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamarey aagey padao kya tha. sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ehram ki haalat mein they lekin main ehram mein nahi tha. logon ne aik gorkhar ko dekha. mein us waqt apna jootaa taankney mein masroof tha. un logon ne mujhey us gorkhar ke mutaalliq bataya kuchh nahi lekin chahtey they ke main kisi tarah dekh loon. chunanche main mutwajjeh hua aur maine usey dekh liya, phir main ghodey ke paas gaya aur usey zeen pehna kar is par Sawar ho gaya lekin kodaa aur neza bhool gaya tha. maine un logon se kaha ke kodaa aur neza mujhey de do. unhon-ne kaha ke nahi Allah ki qism ! ham tumhari shikar ke maamle mein koi madad nahi karengey. (kyonke ham ehram ki haalat mein hain) main ghussa ho gaya aur maine utar kar khud ye donon cheezein uthaaiin phir Sawar ho kar is par hamla kya aur zabah kar liya. jab wo thanda ho gaya to main usey sath laya phir pakka kar maine aur sab ne khaya lekin baad mein unhein shuba hua ke ehram ki haalat mein us ( shikar ka gosht ( khana kaisa hai? phir ham rawaana huey aur maine iska gosht chipa kar rakha. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey to ham ne aap se iske mutaalliq poochha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya, tumharey paas kuchh bacha hua bhi hai? maine wahi dast pesh kya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi usey khaayaa. yahan tak ke iska gosht aap ne apne daanton se kheench kheench kar khaya aur aap ehram mein they Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne bayan kya ke mujh se Zaid-bin-Aslam ne ye waqia bayan kya, unse Ata-bin-Yasar ne aur unse abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ne isi tarah Sara waqia bayan kya."
5408,"unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha aap apne hath se bakri ke shaaney ka gosht kaat kar kha rahe they, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Namaz ke liye bulaya gaya to aap ne gosht aur wo chhuri jis se gosht ki buti kaat rahe they, daal di aur Namaz ke liye khadey ho gaey, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhi aur aap ne nayaa wuzu nahi kya (kyonke aap pahley hi wuzu kiye huey they)."
5409,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kabhi kisi khaney mein koi aib nahi nikaalaa. agar pasand hua to kha liya aur agar na-pasand hua to chhod diya.
5410,"kya tum ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein maida dekha tha? unhon-ne kaha ke nahi, maine puchha kya tum jau ke aatey ko chhaantey they? kaha nahi, balke ham usey sirf phoonk liya kartey they."
5411,aik din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne sahaba ko khajoor taqseem ki aur har shakhs ko saat (7) khajoorein din. mujhey bhi saat (7) khajoorein inayat farmaaiin. unmein aik kharaab thi (aur sakht thi) lekin mujhey wahi sabse zyada achi malum hui kyonke iska chabaanaa mujh ko mushkil ho gaya.
5412,maine apne aapko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath un saat (7) aadmiyon mein se saatwan paya (jinhon ne Islam sabse pahley qabool kya tha) us waqt hamarey paas khaney ke liye yahi keekar ke phal ya patey ke siwa aur kuchh nahi hota. ye khaatey khaatey ham logon ka pakhana bhi bakri ki mengniyon ki tarah ho gaya tha ya ab ye zamana hai ke bani Asad qabeeley ke log mujh ko shariiat ke ehkaam sikhlaatey hain. agar main abhi tak us haal mein hon ke bani Asad ke log mujh ko shariiat ke ehkaam sikhlaayein tab to main tabah hi ho gaya meri mehnat barbad ho gaee.
5413,"maine Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se poochha, kya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kabhi maida khaya tha? unhon-ne kaha ke jab Allah Taala ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Nabi banaya us waqt se wafat tak Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne maida dekha bhi nahi tha. maine puchha kya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein aap ke paas chhalniyaan thin. kaha ke jab Allah Taala ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Nabi banaya us waqt se aap ki wafat tak Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chhalnii dekhi bhi nahi. bayan kya ke maine puchha aap log phir baghair chhanaa hua jau kis tarah khaatey they? batlaya ham usey pees letey they phir usey phoonktey they jo kuchh udnaa hota ud jata aur jo baqi reh jata usey goondh letey (aur pakka kar) kha letey they."
5414,wo kuchh logon ke paas se guzrey jinke samney bhunii hui bakri rakhi thi. unhon-ne unko khaney par bulaya lekin unhon-ne khaney se inkar kar diya aur kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is duniya se rukhsat ho gaey aur aap ne kabhi jau ki roti bhi aasooda ho kar nahi khaaii.
5415,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kabhi mez par khana nahi khaya aur na tashtarii mein 2-4 qism ki cheezein rakh kar khaaiin aur na kabhi chapaatii khaaii. maine Qatada se poochha, phir aap kis cheez par khana khaatey they? batlaya ke Safraa (chamdey ke dastar-khuwaan) par."
5416,Madina hijrat karne ke baad aale-Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kabhi barabar teen din tak gehun ki roti pet bhar kar nahi khaaii yahan tak ke aap duniya se tashrif ley gaey.
5417,jab kisi ghar mein kisi ki wafat ho jati aur uski wjah se auratein jama hotiin aur phir wo chali jaatiin . sirf ghar waley aur khas khas auratein reh jaatiin to aap handi mein talbeena pakaaney ka hukm detiin. wo pakaya jata phir sareed banaya jata aur talbeena is par daala jata. phir Ummul-Momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmaatiin ke isey khaao kyonke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they ke talbeena mareez ke dil ko taskeen deta hai aur uska gham door karta hai.
5418,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mardon main to bahut se kaamil huey lekin aurton mein Maryam binte- Imran aur firaun ki biwi aasiya ke siwa aur koi kaamil nahi hua aur Aaisha ki fazeelat tamam aurton par aisi hai jaisey tamam khaanon par sareed ki fazeelat hai.
5419,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aurton par Aaisha ki fazeelat aisi hai jaisey tamam khaanon par sareed ki fazeelat hai.
5420,main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aap ke aik ghulam ke paas gaya jo darzii they. unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney aik piyala pesh kya jis mein sareed tha. bayan kya ke phir wo apne kaam mein lag gaey. bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usmein se kadu talash karne lagey kaha ke phir main bhi usmein se kadu talash kar karke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney rakhney laga. bayan kya ke iske baad se main bhi kadu bahut pasand karta hun.
5421,ham Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to unki roti pakaaney wala unke paas hi khada tha. unhon-ne kaha ke khaao. main nahi janta ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kabhi patlii roti (chapaatii) dekhi ho. yahan tak ke aap Allah se ja miley aur na Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kabhi musallam bhunii hui bakri dekhi.
5422,"maine dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bakri ke shaane mein se gosht kaat rahe they, phir aap ne usmein se khaayaa. phir aapko Namaz ke liye bulaya gaya to aap khadey ho gaey aur chhuri daal di aur Namaz padhi lekin nayaa wuzu nahi kya."
5423,"maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha kya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teen din se zyada qurbani ka gosht khaney se mana kya hai? unhon-ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aisa kabhi nahi kya. sirf aik saal iska hukm diya tha jis saal qahat padaa tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chaha tha (is hukm ke zariie') ke jo maal waley hain wo (gosht mehfooz karne ke bajaey) mohtajon ko khilaa dein aur ham bakri ke paaey mehfooz rakh letey they aur usey pandarah pandarah din baad khaatey they. unse puchha gaya ke aisa karne ke liye kya majboorii thi? is par Ummul-Momenin (Raziallahu anhu) hans padiin aur farmaya aal Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne saalan ke sath gehun ki roti teen din tak barabar kabhi nahi khaaii yahan tak ke aap Allah se ja miley aur ibne- Kasir ne bayan kya ke hamein Sufiyan ne khabar di, unse Abdur-Rehman bin Aabis ne yahi hadis bayan ki."
5424,(Makka Mukarrama se Haj ki) qurbani ka gosht ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein Madina Munawra latey they. uski mutabiat (pairavi) Muhammad ne ki ibne-Uena ke waaste se aur ibne-Juraij ne bayan kya ke maine Ata se puchha kya Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye bhi kaha tha ke yahan tak ke ham Madina Munawra aa gaey? unhon-ne kaha ke unhon-ne ye nahi kaha tha.
5425,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke apne yahan ke bachchon mein koi bachcha talash kar lao jo mere kaam kar diya kare. chunanche abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) mujhey apni sawari par apne peechhey bitha kar laey. main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki, jab bhi aap kahin padao kartey khidmat karta. main suna karta tha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kasrat se ye dua padha kartey they ( اللهم إني أعوذ بك من الهم والحزن , Mina padhi. والعجز والكسل , Mina padhi. والبخل والجبن وضلع الدين , Mina padhi. وغلبة الرجال ) ''aey Allaah! main teri panah mangta hun gham se, ranj se, ajz se, sustii se, kanjoosii se, buzdili se, qarz ke bojh se aur logon ke ghalba se.'' ( Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke) phir main us waqt se barabar aap ki khidmat karta raha. yahan tak ke ham khaibar se wapas huey aur Safiya-binte-Huyi (Raziallahu anhu) bhi sath thin. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein pasand farmaya tha. main dekhta tha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke liye apni sawari par peechhey kapdey se parda kya aur phir unhein wahan bithaya . aakhir jab maqam sahbaa mein pahunchey to aap ne dastar-khuwaan par hees (khajoor, paneer aur ghi wghaira ka maleeda) banaya phir mujhey bheja aur maine logon ko bula laayaa, phir sab logon ne usey khaayaa. yahi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) se nikah ki dawat walima thi. phir aap rawaana huey aur jab ahad dikhai diya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye pahaad ham se mohabbat rakhta hai aur ham us se mohabbat rakhtey hain. iske baad jab Madina nazar aaya to farmaya ke aey Allaah! main iske donon pahadon ke darmyani ilaaqey ko isi tarah hurmat wala ilaqa banata hun jis tarah Ibrahim ne Makka ko hurmat wala Shahar banaya tha. aey Allaah! iske rehney walon ko barkat ata farmaa. unke mudd main aur unke saa mein barkat farmaa."
5426,ye log Huzefa bin Yamaan (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein maujood they. unhon-ne pani maanga to aik majusi ne unko pani ( chandi ke pyaley mein) la kar diya. jab us ne piyala unke hath mein diya to unhon-ne piyaale ko is par phenk kar maara aur kaha agar maine usey bahut baar us se mana na kya hota (ke chandi soney ke bartan mein mujhey kuchh na diya karo) aagey wo ye farmana chahtey they ke to main us se ye mamla na karta lekin maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai ke resham w deebaa na pahno aur na soney chandi ke bartan mein kuchh piyo aur na unki pleton mein kuchh khaao kyonke ye cheezein un (kuffaar ke liye) duniya mein hain aur hamarey liye aakhirat mein hain.
5427,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us momin ki misal jo Quran padhta ho sangtarey jaisii hai jiski khushbu bhi pakeeza hai aur maza bhi pakeeza hai aur us momin ki misal jo Quran nahi padhta khajoor jaisi hai jis mein koi khushbu nahi hoti lekin maza meethaa hota hai aur munafiq ki misal jo Quran padhta ho, Rehana ( phool ( jaisi hai jiski khushbu to achi hoti hai lekin maza kadwaa hota hai aur jo munafiq Quran bhi nahi padhta uski misal indraayan jaisi hai jis mein koi khushbu nahi hoti aur jiska maza bhi kadwaa hota hai."
5428,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aurton par Aaisha ki fazeelat aisi hai jaisey tamam khaanon par sareed ki fazeelat hai.
5429,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke safar azab ka aik tukda hai, jo insan ko soney aur khaney se rok deta hai. to jab kisi shakhs ki safar ki zarurat mansha ke mutabiq poori ho jaey to usey jald hi ghar wapas aa jana chahiye"
5430,"Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath shariiat ki teen sunnatein qaaim huin. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne unhein (unke maalikon se) khareed kar aazad karna chaha to unke maalikon ne kaha ke 'walaa' ka talluq ham se hi qaaim hoga. ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke) maine iska zikr Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar tum ye shart laga bhi lo jab bhi 'walaa' usi ke sath qaaim hoga jo aazad karega . phir bayan kya ke Barira aazad ki gain aur unhein ikhtiyar diya gaya ke agar wo chaahein to apne shauhar ke sath rahen ya unse alag ho jayen aur teesri baat ye hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik din Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar tashrif laaey, choolhey par handi paak rahi thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne do-pahar ka khana talab farmaya to roti aur ghar mein maujood saalan pesh kya gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke kya maine gosht ( paktey huey) nahi dekha hai? arz kya ke dekha hai ya Rasulullah ! lekin wo gosht to Barira ko sadqe mein mila hai, unhon-ne hamein hadiya ke taur par diya hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unke liye wo sadqa hai lekin hamarey liye hadiya hai."
5431,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) meethii cheez aur shehad pasand farmaya kartey they.
5432,"mein pet bharney ke baad har waqt Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath hi raha karta tha. us waqt mein roti nahi khata tha. na resham pehnta tha, na falan aur fulaanii meri khidmat kartey they ( bhook ki shiddat ki wjah se kabhi-kabhi ( main apne pet par kankariyaan laga leta aur kabhi mein kisi se koi aayat padhney ke liye kehta halanke wo mujhey yad hoti. maqsad sirf ye hota ke wo mujhey apne sath ley jaey aur khana khilaa de aur miskinon ke liye sabse behtreen shakhs Jafar bin abii-Taalib (Raziallahu anhu) they, hamein apne ghar sath ley jatey aur jo kuchh bhi ghar mein hota khilaa detey they. kabhi to aisa hota ke ghi ka dabba nikal kar latey aur is mein kuchh na hota. ham usey phaad kar usmein jo kuchh laga hota chaat letey they."
5433,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne aik darzii ghulam ke paas tashrif le gaey, phir aap ki khidmat main ( pakka hua) kadu pesh kya gaya aur aap usey ( raghbat ke saath) khaney lagey. usi waqt se main bhi kadu pasand karta hun kyonke maine usey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khaatey huey dekha hai."
5434,"jamat Ansar mein aik sahib they jinhein abu-Shuaib kaha jata tha. unke paas aik ghulam tha jo gosht bechtaa tha. abu-Shuaib (Raziallahu anhu) ne un ghulam se kaha ke tum meri taraf se khana taiyaar kar do. main chahta hun ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) samet panch aadmiyon ki dawat karun. chunanche wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko char doosrey aadmiyon ke sath bula kar laey. unke sath aik sahib bhi chalney lagey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ham panch aadmiyon ki tum ne dawat ki hai magar ye sahib bhi hamarey sath aagey hain, agar chaho to unhein ijazat 2 aur agar chaho mana kar do. abu-Shuaib (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine unhein bhi ijazat de di Muhammad-bin Yusuf ne bayan kya ke maine Muhammad-bin Ismail se suna, wo bayan kartey they ke jab log dastar-khuwaan par baithey hon to unhein uski ijazat nahi hai ke aik dastar-khuwaan waley doosrey dastar-khuwaan walon ko apne dastar-khuwaan se utha kar koi cheez dein. albatta aik hi dastar-khuwaan par unke shurakaa ko usmein se koi cheez dene na dene ka ikhtiyar hai."
5435,"mein nau-umr tha aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath rehta tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne aik darzii ghulam ke paas tashrif ley gaey. wo aik piyala laya jis mein khana tha aur uper kadu ke qatley they. aap kadu talash karne lagey. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke jab maine ye dekha to kadu ke qatley aap ke samney jama karke rakhney laga. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke (piyaala Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney rakhney ke baad) ghulam apne kaam mein lag gaya. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke usi waqt se main kadu pasand karne laga, jab maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ye amal dekha."
5436,"aik darzii ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khaney ki dawat di jo unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye taiyaar kya tha. main bhi aap ke sath gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney jau ki roti aur shorba pesh kya gaya. jis mein kadu aur khushk gosht ke tukdey they. maine dekha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) pyaley mein charon taraf kadu talash kar rahe they, isi din se main bhi kadu pasand karne laga."
5437,"maine dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein shorba laya gaya. usmein kadu aur sookhey gosht ke tukdey they, phir maine dekha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usmein se kadu ke qatley talash kar karke kha rahe they."
5438,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aisa kabhi nahi kya ke teen din se zyada gosht qurbani wala rakhney se mana farmaya ho. sirf us saal ye hukm diya tha jis saal qahat ki wjah se log faaqey mein mubtala they. maqsad ye tha ke jo log ghanii hain wo gosht mohtajon ko khilaaein (aur jama karke na rakhein (aur ham to bakri ke paaey mehfooz karke rakh letey they aur pandarah din baad tak ( khaatey they) aur aal Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kabhi saalan ke sath gehun ki roti teen din tak barabar sair ho kar nahi khaaii.
5439,"aik darzii ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khaney ki dawat di jo usney Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye taiyaar kya tha. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke main bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath us dawat mein gaya. unhon-ne aap ki khidmat mein jau ki roti aur shorbaa, jis mein kadu aur khushk kya hua gosht tha, pesh kya. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine dekha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) piyaale mein charon taraf kadu talash kar rahe hain. isi din se main bhi kadu pasand karne laga. shamaama ne bayan kya aur unse Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke phir main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney kadu ke qatley (talaash kar karke) ikatthey karne laga."
5440,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko taaza khajoor kakdi ke sath khaatey dekha hai.
5441,"main Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan saat (7) din tak mehman raha, wo aur unki biwi aur unke khaadim ne raat main (jaagney ki) baari muqarrar kar rakhi thi. raat ke aik tehai hisse mein aik sahib Namaz padhtey rahe phir wo doosrey ko jaga detey aur maine Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne sahaba mein aik martaba khajoor taqseem ki aur mujhey bhi saat (7) khajoorein dein, aik unmein kharaab thi."
5442,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ho gaee aur ham pani aur khajoor hi se (aksar dinon mein) pet bhartey rahe.
5443,"Madina mein aik Yahudi tha aur wo mujhey qarz us shart par diya karta tha ke meri khajoorein taiyaar honey ke waqt ley lega. Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki aik zameen beere-Rooma ke raaste mein thi. aik saal khajoor ke baagh mein phal nahi aaey. phal chuney janey ka jab waqt aaya to wo Yahudi mere paas aaya lekin maine to baagh se kuchh bhi nahi todaa tha. isliye main aainda saal ke liye mohlat maangney laga lekin us ne mohlat deney se inkar kya. iski khabar jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko di gaee to aap ne apne sahaba se farmaya ke chalo , Yahudi se Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye ham mohlat maangengey. chunanche ye sab mere baagh mein tashrif laey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us Yahudi se guftgu farmatey rahe lekin wo yahi kehta raha ke abul-Qaasim mein mohlat nahi de sakta. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye dekha to aap khadey ho gaey aur khajoor ke baagh mein charon taraf phirey phir tashrif laey aur us se guftgu ki lekin us ne ab bhi inkar kya phir main khada hua aur thodi si taaza khajoor la kar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney rakhii. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko khaya phir farmaya Jaabir ! tumhari jhaunpdii kahan hai? maine aapko bataya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usmein mere liye kuchh farsh bichhaa do. maine bichhaa diya to aap dakhil huey aur aaraam farmaya phir bedaar huey to main aik muththii aur khajoor laya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usmein se bhi khaya phir aap khadey huey aur Yahudi se guftgu farmai . us ne ab bhi inkar kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dobara baagh mein khadey huey phir farmaya ke Jaabir ! jao ab phal todo aur qarz ada kar do. aap khajooron ke todey janey ki jagah khadey ho gaey aur maine baagh mein se itni khajoorein tod lin jin se maine qarz ada kar diya aur is mein se khajoorein bach bhi gaee phir main wahan se nikla aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar ye khushkhabri sunai to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya main gawahi deta hun ke main Allah ka rasool hun. abu-Adbullah imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke us hadis mein jo ( عروش (ka lafz hai) عروش (aur ( عريش ( Imaarat ki chhat ko kehtey hain. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke (sura Al-Anaam mein lafz) (ma'rooshaat) se murad angoor wghaira ki tattiyaan hain. dusri aayat (sura al-Baqara) ( عروشها خاویة ( yani apni chhaton par girey huey."
5444,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein baithey huey they ke khajoor ke darakht ka gaabha laya gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kuchh darakht aisey hotey hain jinki barkat musalman ki barkat ki tarah hoti hai. maine khayal kya ke aap ka ishara khajoor ke darakht ki taraf hai. maine sochaa ke keh dun ke wo darakht khajoor ka hota hai, ya Rasulullah ! lekin phir jo maine mud kar dekha to majlis mein mere ilawa nau (9) aadmi aur they aur main unmein sabse chhota tha. isliye main khamosh raha phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo darakht khajoor ka hai."
5445,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jisne har din subah ke waqt saat (7) ajwa khajoorein kha liin, usey us din na zahar nuqsan pahuncha sakega aur na jaadoo."
5446,hamein Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath (jab wo hijaaz ke khaleefa they) aik saal qahat ka saamnaa karna padaa to unhon-ne raashan mein hamein khaney ke liye khajoorein din. Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey paas se guzartey aur ham khajoor khaatey hotey to wo farmatey ke 2 khajooron ko aik sath mila kar na khaao kyonke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 khajooron ko aik sath mila kar khaney se mana kya hai. phir farmaya siwa is sura ke jab usko khaney wala shakhs apne sathi se (jo khaney mein Sharik hai) uski ijazat ley ley. Shoba ne bayan kya ke ijazat wala tukda ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ka qaul hai.
5447,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khajoor ko kakdi ke sath khaatey huey dekha.
5448,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke darakhton mein aik darakht misl musalman ke hai aur wo khajoor ka darakht hai.
5449,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kakdi ke sath khajoor khaatey huey dekha hai.
5450,"unki walida Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik mudd jau liya aur unse pees kar iska ( خطيفة ( ) aatey ko doodh mein mila kar pakaatey hain) pakaya aur unke paas jo ghi ka dabba tha usmein is par se ghi nichodaa, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat main (bulaaney ke liye) bhejaa. main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein gaya to aap apne sahaba ke sath tashrif rakhtey they. maine aapko khana khaney ke liye bulaya. aap ne malum farmaya aur wo log bhi jo mere sath hain? chunanche main wapas aaya aur kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) to farmatey hain ke jo mere sath maujood hain wo bhi chalengey. is par abu-Talha Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! wo to aik cheez hai jo Umme-Sulaim ne aap ke liye pakaaii hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aur khana aap ke paas laya gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke das aadmiyon ko mere paas andar bula lo. chunanche das sahaba dakhil huey aur khana pet bhar kar khaya phir farmaya das aadmiyon ko mere paas aur bula lo. ye das bhi andar aaey aur pet bhar kar khaya phir farmaya aur das aadmiyon ko bula lo. is tarah unhon-ne chalis (40) aadmiyon ka shumaar kya. iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khana khaya phir aap khadey huey to main dekhney laga ke khaney mein se kuchh bhi kam nahi hua."
5451,Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko lehsun ke barey mein kuchh kehtey nahi suna. albatta Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs ( lehsun ( khaaey to wo hamari masjid ke qareeb na aaey.
5452,"Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey they ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jisne lehsun ya piyaz khaaii ho to usey chahiye ke ham se door rahe, ya ye farmaya ke hamari masjid se door rahe."
5453,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath maqam marruz-zohraan par they, ham peelu tod rahe they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo khub kala ho wo todo kyonke wo zyada lazeez hota hai. Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya aap ne bakriyan charaaii hain? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, aur koi Nabi aisa nahi guzra jisne bakriyan na charaaii hun."
5454,"ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath khaibar rawaana huey. jab ham maqam sahbaa par pahunchey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khana talab farmaya, khaney mein sattu ke siwa aur koi cheez nahi laai gaee, phir ham ne khana khaya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kulli karke Namaz ke liye khadey ho gaey, ham ne bhi kulli ki."
5455,ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath khaibar ki taraf nikley jab ham maqam sahbaa par pahunchey . Yahya ne kaha ke ye jagah khaibar se aik manzil ki doori par hai to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khana talab farmaya lekin sattu ke siwa aur koi cheez nahi laai gaee. ham ne usey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath khaya phir aap ne hamein maghrib ki Namaz padhai aur nayaa wuzu nahi kya aur Sufiyan ne kaha maano ke tum ye hadis Yahya hi se sun rahe ho.
5456,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab koi shakhs khana khaaey to hath chaatney ya kisi ko chataaney se pahley hath na poonchhey .
5457,Saeed bin al-Haaris ne Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se aisi cheez ke (khaaney ke baad) jo aag par rakhi ho wuzu ke mutaalliq puchha (ke kya aisi cheez khaney se wuzu toot jata hai? ( to unhon-ne kaha ke nahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein hamein is tarah ka khana (jo pakka hua hota ( bahut kam muyassar aata tha aur agar muyassar aa bhi jata tha to siwa hamari hatheliyon baazuon aur paon ke koi roomaal nahi hota tha (aur ham unhein se apne hath saaf karke ( Namaz padh letey they aur wuzu .
5458,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney se jab khana uthaya jata to aap ye dua padhtey الحمد لله كثيرا طيبا مباركا فيه ، Mina padhi. غير مكفي ، Mina wla مودع wla مستغنى عنه ، Mina ربنا ''tamaam ta'reefein Allah ke liye, bahut zyada pakeeza barkat wali , ham us khaney ka haq poori tarah ada na kar sakey aur ye hamesha ke liye rukhsat nahi kya gaya hai (aur ye isliye kaha taake (us se ham ko be-parwaaii ka khayal na ho, aey hamarey rab!''"
5459,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab khaney se farigh hotey aur aik martaba bayan kya ke jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apna dastar-khuwaan uthatey ye dua padhtey لحمد لله الذي كفانا وأروانا ، Mina غير مكفي ، Mina wla مكفور ، وقال Murra الحمد لله ربنا ، Mina غير مكفي ، Mina wla مودع ، wla مستغنى ، Mina ربنا‏ ''tamaam ta'reefein us Allah ke liye hain jisne hamari kifaayat ki aur hamein sairaab kya. ham us khaney ka haq poori tarah ada na kar sakey warna ham is nemat ke munkar nahi hain. aur aik martaba farmaya '' terey hi liye tamam ta'reefein hain aey hamarey rab! iska haq ada nahi kar sakey aur na ye hamesha ke liye rukhsat kya gaya hai. (ye isliye kaha taake) us se ham ko be niyaazii ka khayal na ho. aey hamarey rab! '' .
5460,"maine Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab tum mein kisi shakhs ka khaadim uska khana laey to agar wo usey apne sath nahi bitha sakta to kam se kam aik ya 2 luqma us khaney mein se usey khilaa de (kyonke) us ne (pakaatey waqt) uski garmi aur taiyaarii ki mashaqqat bardasht ki hai."
5461,"jamat Ansar ke aik sahabi abu-Shuaib (Raziallahu anhu) ke naam se mashhoor they. unke paas aik ghulam tha jo gosht bechaa karta tha. wo sahabi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki majlis mein hazir huey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne sahaba ke sath tashrif rakhtey they. unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehre se faaqa ka andaza laga liya. chunanche wo apne gosht bechney waaley ghulam ke paas gaey aur kaha ke mere liye panch aadmiyon ka khana taiyaar kar do. main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko char doosrey aadmiyon ke sath dawat doonga. ghulam ne khana taiyaar kar diya. iske baad abu-Shuaib (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein gaey aur aapko khaney ki dawat di. unke sath aik aur sahib bhi chalney lagey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey abu-Shuaib ! ye sahib bhi hamarey sath aagey hain, agar tum chaho to unhein bhi ijazat de do aur agar chaho to chhod do. unhon-ne arz kya nahi balke mein unhein bhi ijazat deta hun."
5462,"unhon-ne dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne hath se bakri ke shaaney ka gosht kaat-kaat kar kha rahe they, phir aapko Namaz ke liye bulaya gaya to aap gosht aur chhuri jis se aap kaat rahe they, chhod kar khadey ho gaey aur Namaz padhai aur us Namaz ke liye nayaa wuzu nahi kya."
5463,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab raat ka khana samney rakh diya gaya ho aur Namaz bhi khadi ho gaee ho to pahley khana khaao aur Ayub se riwayat hai, unse Naafe ne, unse ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usi ke mutaabiq."
5464,ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik martaba raat ka khana khaya aur us waqt aap imam ki qirat sun rahe they.
5465,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab Namaz khadi ho chukey aur raat ka khana bhi samney ho to khana khaao. Wuhaib aur Yahya-bin-Saeed ne bayan kya, unse Hisham ne ke jab raat ka khana rakha ja chukey."
5466,main parde ke hukm ke barey mein zyada janta hun. Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) bhi mujh se iske barey mein puchha kartey they. Zainab-binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anhu) se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki shadi ka mauqa tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse nikah Madina Munawra mein kya tha. din chadhney ke baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon ki khaney ki dawat ki thi. aap baithey huey they aur aap ke sath kuchh aur sahaba bhi baithey huey they. us waqt tak doosrey log (khaaney se farigh ho kar) ja chukey they. aakhir aap bhi khadey ho gaey aur chaltey rahe. main bhi aap ke sath chalta raha. aap Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke hujrey par pahunchey phir aap ne khayal kya ke wo log (bhi jo khaney ke baad ghar baithey reh gaey they) ja chukey hongey (is liye aap wapas tashrif laaey) main bhi aap ke sath wapas aaya lekin wo log ab bhi usi jagah baithey huey they. aap phir wapas aa gaey. main bhi aap ke sath dobara wapas aaya. aap Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke hujre par pahunchey phir aap wahan se wapas huey. mein bhi aap ke sath tha. ab wo log ja chukey they. iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne aur mere darmyan parda latkaayaa aur parde ki aayat nazil hui.
